description:
• This course will help you to self manage you own career and develop your skills to
    consistently self manage your reputation.
  • If you are keen to develop your personal brand and proactively secure job
    opportunities or get promoted, this course is for you.
  • The programme has been designed on the basis of the core tactics top performers
    use to successfully climb the career ladder

There are 5 easy to use modules along with downloadable materials for each to work through. They are designed to challenge your thinking and become more self aware of your personal attributes and highlight the areas which may be catching you out. You will be better prepared to promote yourself at future formal and informal meetings and articulate your strengths, achievements and what you want from future work opportunities

The modules build your self awareness and develop your personal brand step by step.

It is advisable you complete the modules in order. The downloadable materials in each section are available to print as a workbook.

Depending on how long you take to consider your answers to the questions in the downloadable materials, the course can be completed in half a day.
title: Use Your Personal Brand to Navigate Your Career
